title: Drawing, "End Table with Cabinet", ca. 1930
medium: Graphite and red color pencil on tracing paper, ruled border in graphite
inscribed: Inscribed in graphite at lower right: SCALE 1 1/2"=1'/ SEE uphols #9212; inscribed dimensions
description: Perspective, plan, and elevation drawing for end table. Rounded left edge and top surface; two shelves on left side. Cabinet on right side with vertical and rectangular drawer pull. Perspective drawing of cabinet against side of sofa. Curve of left side matches curve of sofa arm.
